OL,4,CRev Richard Coles: Partner's alcoholism
OL,5,Clike 'a demon'
OL,6, The Reverend Richard Coles has said his
OL,7, late partner's alcoholism was as if he
OL,8, was being "seized by a demon".
OL,10,FThe Reverend David Coles died in
OL,11,FDecember 2019 at Kettering General
OL,12,FHospital after what was initially
OL,13,Fdescribed as "a long illness".
OL,15,FRichard Coles, a vicar in
OL,16,FNorthamptonshire, has now said it was
OL,17,Falcohol that killed his partner.
OL,19,FThe BBC broadcaster said: "Anyone who
OL,20,Fhas loved an addict and lived with an
OL,21,Faddict will know how tough it is."
